                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="col-12">
                        <div class="d-flex align-items-center mb-4">
                            <div class="bg-success text-white rounded-circle d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center me-4 flex-shrink-0"
                                style="width: 60px; height: 60px;">
                                <i class="fas fa-cogs fs-4"></i>
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <h5 class="fw-bold mb-2">2. AI Analyzes Your Taste</h5>
                                <p class="mb-0 text-muted">Our machine learning algorithms analyze patterns in your
